      <div class="prose">

        <p>Homebuilders face a unique combination of challenges: managing hundreds of owner selections per home, coordinating 15–25 subcontractors per project, maintaining client relationships through 8–18 month build cycles, and tracking financials against a complex budget. The right software addresses all of these — not just one or two.</p>

        <h2>What homebuilders need that other contractors don't</h2>
        <ul>
          <li><strong>Selections management:</strong> Tracking every owner decision — flooring, fixtures, cabinet hardware, countertop material, appliances — with allowance tracking and timestamped approvals</li>
          <li><strong>Long-horizon scheduling:</strong> 12–18 month project schedules with multi-trade dependencies and weather contingencies</li>
          <li><strong>Client portal:</strong> Homeowners need transparency during a build that's their largest financial and emotional investment</li>
          <li><strong>Warranty management:</strong> Post-closing warranty item tracking and resolution for production builders</li>
          <li><strong>Multi-project visibility:</strong> Most custom builders run 5–30 concurrent projects</li>
        </ul>

        <h2>Top picks for homebuilders</h2>

        <h3>Buildertrend — The clear market leader for homebuilders</h3>
        <p>Buildertrend is the dominant platform for residential homebuilders and has been for over a decade. It was built specifically for this use case — the client portal, selections management, scheduling, and change order workflow are all designed for the homebuilding context in a way that no other platform matches.</p>

        <ul>
          <li>Comprehensive selections management with allowance tracking and client approval records</li>
          <li>Industry-leading client portal — homeowners see schedules, approve selections, sign COs, and make payments</li>
          <li>Gantt scheduling with automatic cascade when tasks shift</li>
          <li>Warranty management module for post-close items (Complete plan)</li>
          <li>Lead management for pre-sale relationship tracking (Complete plan)</li>
          <li>Unlimited users — subs, staff, and clients all included</li>
        </ul>

        <blockquote>
          <p>"The client portal alone changed how we build. Our clients feel informed, not anxious. The 'how's my house going?' calls dropped by 80% when we launched Buildertrend." — Custom homebuilder, 40 homes/year</p>
        </blockquote>

